01:05:31.030 --> 01:05:33.763
What would happen if
it said, hey, this

01:05:33.763 --> 01:05:35.680
is good for the environment,
too, as part of--

01:05:35.680 --> 01:05:37.930
RICHARD SCHMALENSEE: I think
the environmental-- well,

01:05:37.930 --> 01:05:39.160
it's not a bill yet.

01:05:39.160 --> 01:05:42.650
There's no point in introducing
a bill into this Congress.

01:05:42.650 --> 01:05:45.190
There will be-- it is expected--

01:05:45.190 --> 01:05:51.160
the expectation is that after
the election, when there's

01:05:51.160 --> 01:05:55.720
