are capable of words

01:06:29.290 --> 01:06:30.920
of more than one syllable.

01:06:30.920 --> 01:06:35.860
So some of those folks would
be pushed to opposition.

01:06:35.860 --> 01:06:37.480
If you don't mention
climate, they

01:06:37.480 --> 01:06:39.700
